{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"关于","page":{"layout":"document","title":"CUPTI 通用辅助文件","description":"GitHub 仓库和完整教程可在 <https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/cupti-tutorial 获取。","bodyHtml":"<blockquote>\n<p>GitHub 仓库和完整教程可在 <a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/cupti-tutorial\">https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/cupti-tutorial</a> 获取。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"概述\">概述</h2>\n<p>此目录包含在多个CUPTI示例中使用的共享辅助文件和工具。这些文件为CUPTI初始化、错误处理、活动记录处理和其他常用操作提供通用功能。</p>\n<h2 id=\"文件\">文件</h2>\n<h3 id=\"helper_cuptih\">helper_cupti.h</h3>\n<p>一个全面的头文件，提供：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>错误处理宏</strong>：简化CUPTI和CUDA API调用的错误检查</li>\n<li><strong>通用初始化函数</strong>：CUPTI性能分析的标准设置例程</li>\n<li><strong>内存管理工具</strong>：安全分配和释放辅助函数</li>\n<li><strong>设备管理函数</strong>：GPU设备枚举和选择工具</li>\n</ul>\n<p>主要宏和函数包括：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"cpp\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"cpp\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">// 错误检查宏</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">#define</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> CUPTI_API_CALL</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">(</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">apiFuncCall</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">)</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">#define</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> RUNTIME_API_CALL</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">(</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">apiFuncCall</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">)  </span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">#define</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> DRIVER_API_CALL</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">(</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">apiFuncCall</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">)</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">#define</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> MEMORY_ALLOCATION_CALL</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">(</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">var</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">)</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">// 通用初始化</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">void</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> initCuda</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">void</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> cleanupCuda</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">CUdevice</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> pickDevice</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h3 id=\"helper_cupti_activityh\">helper_cupti_activity.h</h3>\n<p>用于CUPTI活动记录处理的扩展头文件：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>活动记录管理</strong>：处理不同活动类型的结构和函数</li>\n<li><strong>缓冲区管理</strong>：活动记录的高效缓冲区分配和处理</li>\n<li><strong>回调注册</strong>：设置CUPTI回调的工具</li>\n<li><strong>数据提取</strong>：从活动记录中提取有意义数据的辅助函数</li>\n<li><strong>输出格式化</strong>：用于美化打印性能分析结果的函数</li>\n</ul>\n<p>主要功能包括：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"cpp\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"cpp\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">// 活动记录处理</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">void</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> processActivityRecord</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">(</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">CUpti_Activity</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">*</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">);</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">void</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> handleActivityBuffer</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">(</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">uint8_t*</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\"> buffer</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">, </span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">size_t</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\"> validSize</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">);</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">// 缓冲区管理</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">CUpti_BufferAlloc bufferRequested;</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">CUpti_BufferCompleted bufferCompleted;</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">// 回调工具</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">void</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> enableActivityRecords</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">void</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> registerCallbacks</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"在示例中的使用\">在示例中的使用</h2>\n<p>这些辅助文件包含在大多数CUPTI示例中，用于：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>减少代码重复</strong>：通用操作被集中化</li>\n<li><strong>简化错误处理</strong>：在示例中实现一致的错误检查</li>\n<li><strong>标准化初始化</strong>：统一的CUPTI设置程序</li>\n<li><strong>简化活动处理</strong>：可重用的活动记录处理</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"典型包含模式\">典型包含模式</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"cpp\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"cpp\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">#include</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> \"helper_cupti.h\"</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">#include</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> \"helper_cupti_activity.h\"</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">int</span><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">() {</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">    // 初始化CUDA和CUPTI</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\">    initCuda</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">    </span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">    // 设置性能分析</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\">    enableActivityRecords</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\">    registerCallbacks</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">    </span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">    // 运行您的应用程序代码</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\">    runKernels</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">    </span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">    // 处理结果并清理</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\">    processResults</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#DCBDFB\">    cleanupCuda</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">();</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">    </span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F47067\">    return</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> 0</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">;</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">}</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"与示例的集成\">与示例的集成</h2>\n<p>此仓库中的大多数示例通过以下方式使用这些辅助器：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>包含适当的头文件</li>\n<li>在main()中调用初始化函数</li>\n<li>在整个代码中使用错误检查宏</li>\n<li>利用活动处理工具</li>\n<li>遵循标准清理程序</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"自定义\">自定义</h2>\n<p>虽然这些辅助器提供通用功能，但个别示例可能：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>扩展提供的结构</li>\n<li>添加特定于示例的处理函数</li>\n<li>自定义回调处理程序</li>\n<li>实现额外的错误处理</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"好处\">好处</h2>\n<p>使用这些通用辅助器提供：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>一致性</strong>：所有示例遵循相似模式</li>\n<li><strong>可靠性</strong>：经过良好测试的错误处理和初始化</li>\n<li><strong>可维护性</strong>：对通用功能的更改影响所有示例</li>\n<li><strong>学习性</strong>：清晰的CUPTI最佳实践示例</li>\n<li><strong>效率</strong>：优化的缓冲区管理和处理</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"贡献\">贡献</h2>\n<p>在添加新示例或修改现有示例时：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>尽可能使用现有的辅助函数</li>\n<li>将新的通用功能添加到适当的辅助文件中</li>\n<li>保持一致的错误处理模式</li>\n<li>添加新辅助器时更新文档</li>\n<li>跨多个示例测试更改以确保兼容性</li>\n</ol>\n<p>这些辅助文件对于在CUPTI示例套件中保持一致性和可靠性至关重要。</p>","headings":[{"id":"概述","text":"概述","depth":2},{"id":"文件","text":"文件","depth":2},{"id":"helper_cuptih","text":"helper_cupti.h","depth":3},{"id":"helper_cupti_activityh","text":"helper_cupti_activity.h","depth":3},{"id":"在示例中的使用","text":"在示例中的使用","depth":2},{"id":"典型包含模式","text":"典型包含模式","depth":2},{"id":"与示例的集成","text":"与示例的集成","depth":2},{"id":"自定义","text":"自定义","depth":2},{"id":"好处","text":"好处","depth":2},{"id":"贡献","text":"贡献","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/others/cupti-tutorial/common/README.zh.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2025-06-22T05:40:48.000Z","createdAt":"2025-06-22T05:40:48.000Z","authors":[{"name":"github-actions[bot]","email":"41898282+github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com"}]},"path":"/zh/others/cupti-tutorial/common/","alternates":{"en":"/others/cupti-tutorial/common/","zh":"/zh/others/cupti-tutorial/common/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"About Eunomia","description":"The broader Eunomia project family, including GPU tutorials, research notes, experiments, and related open-source tools.","href":"/zh/others/"},"previous":{"title":"CUPTI 检查点 API 教程","description":"完整的 GitHub 仓库和教程请访问 <https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/cupti-tutorial。","href":"/zh/others/cupti-tutorial/checkpoint_kernels/"},"next":{"title":"CUPTI 并发分析教程","description":"GitHub 仓库和完整教程可在 <https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/cupti-tutorial 获取。","href":"/zh/others/cupti-tutorial/concurrent_profiling/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"About Eunomia","items":[{"title":"About Eunomia","href":"/zh/others/","depth":0},{"title":"BPF-Benchmark","href":"/zh/others/bpf-benchmark/","depth":1},{"title":"bpf-compatible","href":"/zh/others/bpf-compatible/","depth":1},{"title":"Contributing to eunomia-bpf","href":"/zh